  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deadly Heart Gambit is a First-Person Anime Gambling Visual Novel.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alice-sama</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A very fun card game (created by Alice-sama)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 chapters of story (featuring Alice-sama)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 endings and 1 hidden secret</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Time is running out</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I know. The doctor said you have only 3 months left to live. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You want to gamble for more time. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The game is very simple</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202110/extras/417aea0252a78ef8e92d078ba0adbf04.avif?t=1772211122\" width=780 height=256 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I will give you time for every card you draw.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>However</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202110/extras/e6c96f4227c468020f8c069733816e2a.avif?t=1772211122\" width=780 height=256 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You lose your time when you draw a joker.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you lose all your time, your heart will be mine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>How to avoid losing</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202110/extras/05ed0d8abd7942f1c324e49821237922.avif?t=1772211122\" width=780 height=256 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You keep every card you draw. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can pass your turn by playing a card.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But you don’t want to avoid losing to me, because you want to give me your heart, right?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Are you sure you want to leave?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202110/extras/c879f3e6472f4e7f02bada71bdedcc13.avif?t=1772211122\" width=780 height=256 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I’ll give you more time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join me in an eternal game, where we play forever.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >just me and you</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >forever</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >alice forever</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >alice forever alice forever</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >alice forever alice forever alice forever</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >alice forever alice forever alice forever alice forever</p>",
